5911.name: Unknown
5911.message:
You cannot create any more
communities.

To create a new community, you
must delete an existing one first.
5911.short_description: Cannot create anymore communities due to max being reached.
5911.long_description: The maximum of communities has been reached, making impossible the creation of new ones.
5911.long_solution: Delete an existing community to make space for new ones and try again.
